trans-unit.source: Represents an extensibility element added to an <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.InputBinding"></xref> or an <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OutputBinding"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Representerer et extensibility-element som er lagt til en <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.InputBinding"> </xref> eller en <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OutputBinding"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a string containing a list of space-delimited URIs.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en streng som inneholder en liste over mellomrom URIer.

trans-unit.source: The URIs represent the encoding style (or styles) to be used to encode messages within the SOAP body.
trans-unit.target: URIer representerer koding stilen (eller stiler) brukes til å kryptere meldinger i SOAP-meldingsteksten.

trans-unit.source: The value of this property should be set only if the value of the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding.Use%2A> property is `Encoded`.
trans-unit.target: Verdien for denne egenskapen kan bare angis hvis verdien for den <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding.Use%2A>egenskapen `Encoded`.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding.Use%2A>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise this property value will be ignored.
trans-unit.target: Hvis ignoreres denne egenskapsverdien.

trans-unit.source: A string containing a list of URIs.
trans-unit.target: En streng som inneholder en liste over URIer.

trans-unit.source: The default value is an empty string ("").
trans-unit.target: Standardverdien er en tom streng ("").

trans-unit.source: Get or sets the URI representing the location of the specifications for encoding of content not specifically defined by the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding.Encoding*> property.
trans-unit.target: Får eller angir URIEN som representerer plasseringen til spesifikasjonene for kodingen for innhold som ikke er spesielt som er definert av den <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding.Encoding*>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding.Encoding*>

trans-unit.source: This property will return an empty string ("") if the property value has not been set.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen vil returnere en tom streng ("") Hvis egenskapsverdien ikke er angitt.

trans-unit.source: The value should only be set if the value of the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding.Use%2A> property is `Encoded`.
trans-unit.target: Verdien kan bare angis hvis verdien for den <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding.Use%2A>egenskapen `Encoded`.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding.Use%2A>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise the property value will be ignored, thus leading to unexpected behavior by the XML Web service.
trans-unit.target: Ellers ignoreres egenskapsverdien dermed noe som fører til uventede resultater av XML-webtjenesten.

trans-unit.source: A string containing a URI.
trans-unit.target: En streng som inneholder en URI.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value indicating which parts of the transmitted message appear within the SOAP body portion of the transmission.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir hvilke deler av den overførte meldingen vises i SOAP-brødtekst av overføring.

trans-unit.source: Some parts of the transmitted message can appear in portions other than the SOAP body, such as when SOAP is used with a <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimeMultipartRelatedBinding>.
trans-unit.target: Deler av den overførte meldingen kan vises i deler enn SOAP-teksten, for eksempel når SOAP brukes med en <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimeMultipartRelatedBinding>.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimeMultipartRelatedBinding>

trans-unit.source: In such a case, the other members of the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart.Extensions%2A> property determine the locations of the other parts of the message.
trans-unit.target: I slike tilfeller andre medlemmer av den <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart.Extensions%2A>egenskapen fastslå plasseringen av de andre delene av meldingen.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart.Extensions%2A>

trans-unit.source: This property returns exactly the same information as the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding.PartsString%2A> property, but the results are returned within an array rather than within a space-delimited string.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen returnerer nøyaktig den samme informasjonen som den <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding.PartsString%2A>egenskapen, men resultatet returneres i en matrise i stedet for i en streng mellomrom som skilletegn.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding.PartsString%2A>

trans-unit.source: A string array containing the names of the appropriate message parts.
trans-unit.target: En strengmatrise som inneholder navnene på delene melding.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value indicating which parts of the transmitted message appear within the SOAP body portion of the transmission.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir hvilke deler av den overførte meldingen vises i SOAP-brødtekst av overføring.

trans-unit.source: Some parts of the transmitted message can appear in portions other than the SOAP body, such as when SOAP is used with a <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimeMultipartRelatedBinding>.
trans-unit.target: Deler av den overførte meldingen kan vises i deler enn SOAP-teksten, for eksempel når SOAP brukes med en <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimeMultipartRelatedBinding>.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimeMultipartRelatedBinding>

trans-unit.source: In such a case, the other members of the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart.Extensions%2A> property determine the locations of other parts of the message.
trans-unit.target: I slike tilfeller andre medlemmer av den <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart.Extensions%2A>egenskapen fastslå plasseringen av andre deler av meldingen.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart.Extensions%2A>

trans-unit.source: This property returns exactly the same information as the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding.Parts%2A> property, but the results are returned within a space-delimited string rather than within an array.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen returnerer nøyaktig den samme informasjonen som den <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding.Parts%2A>egenskapen, men resultatet returneres i en streng mellomrom som skilletegn i stedet for i en matrise.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding.Parts%2A>

trans-unit.source: PartsString is used internally for xml serialization and shouldn't be called directly.
trans-unit.target: PartsString brukes internt for xml-serialisering og bør ikke kalles direkte.

trans-unit.source: To return the transmitted message parts appearing within the SOAP body portion of the transmission, use the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding.Parts%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil returnere overførte meldingen delene vises i SOAP-brødtekst av overføringen, kan du bruke den <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding.Parts%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding.Parts%2A>

trans-unit.source: A space-delimited string containing the appropriate message parts.
trans-unit.target: En mellomrom streng som inneholder delene melding.

trans-unit.source: Indicates whether the message parts are encoded using specified encoding rules, or define the concrete schema of the message.
trans-unit.target: Angir om meldingen delene kodes ved hjelp av angitt koding regler eller definerer konkrete skjemaet for meldingen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding.Namespace%2A> and <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding.Encoding%2A> properties depend on the value of this property.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding.Namespace%2A>og <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding.Encoding%2A>Egenskaper som er avhengig av verdien for denne egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding.Encoding%2A> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding.Namespace%2A>

trans-unit.source: Their values should be set only if the value of this property is `Encoded`.
trans-unit.target: Verdiene kan bare angis hvis verdien for denne egenskapen er `Encoded`.

trans-unit.source: Otherwise the XML Web service will produce unexpected behavior.
trans-unit.target: XML-webtjenesten produsere ellers uforutsette virkemåter.

trans-unit.source: One of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBindingUse"></xref> values.
trans-unit.target: Én av de <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBindingUse"> </xref> verdier.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_Default" name="Default" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standard <xref uid="langword_csharp_Default" name="Default" href=""> </xref>.
